text:
They've now moved to a small corner on the 3rd floor of the Medical Centre side of the building. It's more like a pop up stall, right by the lift lobby, which suffices, but it feels a little restrictive at the same time.

If you need a pharmacy, 3rd floor of the medical centre lift lobby!

Guardian@MEH Orchard. Get to know them. Staffs are generally pleasant. Small space, limited items, but convenient to get prescriptions and can get reasonable service from promoters. Pharmacy pleasant and efficient. Cannot do without this outlet at MtE Orchard.
